title: Packers-Vikings MNF Preview; Can Kirk Cousins win in primetime? (Football 12/23)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Jared Dubin to preview Packers vs. Vikings on Monday Night Football. First, the guys discuss the Cowboys' failures (1:15) and then get into the MNF matchup (8:00), discussing the Packers' path to 11-3, what to make of Aaron Rodgers' season, Dalvin Cook's injury impact and Kirk Cousins in primetime.
